Description: Minecraft launcher with mod support and server management
 SuperLauncher is a modern Minecraft launcher with:
  * Mod installation from Modrinth and CurseForge
  * Local server creation and management
  * Instance management for multiple profiles
  * Built-in skin system
  * Discord Rich Presence integration
  * Modern glass-morphism UI
 .
 This package contains the Python edition.

